'''阮文平'''（{{lang-vi|'''Nguyễn Văn Bình'''}}，{{bd|1961年|3月4日}}），生於[[越南|越南]][[富寿省|富寿省]]，[[越南|越南]]政治人物。曾任[[越南共产党|越南共产党]]第十二届[[中央政治局委员|中央政治局委员]]、[[越南共产党中央书记处|越南共产党中央书记处]]书记、中央经济部部长<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cn.nhandan.com.vn/political/item/5562101-%E8%B6%8A%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%83%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%BF%E9%98%AE%E6%96%87%E5%B9%B3%E4%BC%9A%E8%A7%81%E4%BD%BF%E5%91%BD2020%E5%80%A1%E8%AE%AE%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC.html |title=越共中央经济部部长阮文平会见使命2020倡议领导 |accessdate=2020-09-21 |archive-date=2018-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620101215/http://cn.nhandan.com.vn/political/item/5562101-%E8%B6%8A%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%83%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%BF%E9%98%AE%E6%96%87%E5%B9%B3%E4%BC%9A%E8%A7%81%E4%BD%BF%E5%91%BD2020%E5%80%A1%E8%AE%AE%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年8月3日，任[[越南国家银行|越南国家银行]]行长<ref name="行长">{{Cite web |url=http://cafef.vn/tai-chinh-ngan-hang/ong-nguyen-van-binh-chinh-thuc-lam-thong-doc-ngan-hang-nha-nuoc-20110803105439149.chn |title=Ông Nguyễn Văn Bình chính thức làm Thống đốc Ngân hàng Nhà nước |accessdate=2015-05-23 |date=2011-03-08 |publisher='''''cafef.vn''''' |pages= |language=vi |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523184838/http://cafef.vn/tai-chinh-ngan-hang/ong-nguyen-van-binh-chinh-thuc-lam-thong-doc-ngan-hang-nha-nuoc-20110803105439149.chn |archivedate=2015-05-23 |quote=Ngày 03/8/2011, kỳ họp thứ nhất khóa XIII Quốc hội nước Cộng hòa xã hội chủ nghĩa Việt Nam đã bỏ phiếu phê chuẩn bổ nhiệm các thành viên của Chính phủ theo đề nghị của Thủ tướng Chính phủ Nguyễn Tấn Dũng. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2016年1月27日，越共十二大上连任中央政治局委员。2016年4月11日，阮文平任中央经济部部长<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cn.dangcongsan.vn/news/%E9%98%AE%E6%96%87%E5%B9%B3%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E8%B6%8A%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%83%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%BF-382173.html |title=阮文平担任越共中央经济部部长 |accessdate=2020-09-21 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713041737/http://cn.dangcongsan.vn/news/%E9%98%AE%E6%96%87%E5%B9%B3%E6%8B%85%E4%BB%BB%E8%B6%8A%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%83%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%BF-382173.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年11月6日，阮文平因在[[越南国家银行|越南国家银行]]行长任期内违反民主集中制原则和工作规则；失职失责、管理不严、检查监督不到位，在颁发和组织履行一些关于银行信贷业务的决议、规定和决定中出现许多违法违规行为，造成严重后果而受到[[越共中央政治局|越共中央政治局]]警告处分。2021年1月，不再担任越共中央政治局委员、中央经济部长。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://baochinhphu.vn/Hoat-dong-cua-lanh-dao-Dang-Nha-nuoc/Tong-Bi-thu-Chu-tich-nuoc-Nguyen-Phu-Trong-trao-quyet-dinh-phan-cong-Uy-vien-Bo-Chinh-tri/422450.vgp|title=Tổng Bí thư, Chủ tịch nước Nguyễn Phú Trọng trao quyết định phân công Ủy viên Bộ Chính trị||archivedate=2021-02-06|website=Báo điện tử Chính phủ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206055034/http://baochinhphu.vn/Hoat-dong-cua-lanh-dao-Dang-Nha-nuoc/Tong-Bi-thu-Chu-tich-nuoc-Nguyen-Phu-Trong-trao-quyet-dinh-phan-cong-Uy-vien-Bo-Chinh-tri/422450.vgp|language=vi}}</ref>

